  "texts": [
    "Therefore, in a reasoning process, if the model generates two full solution trees, the maximum number of reasoning rounds is 30, as shown in Figure 7.",
    "We report the statistics of seed data in Table 8, which is the intra-category multi-tool instruction subset from ToolBench (Qin et al., 2023).",
    "It is the most challenging subset in ToolBench.",
    "It requires the combined use of multiple tools from different categories, which helps to reflect complex realworld scenarios.",
    "We removed seed tasks that did not provide a proper candidate tag list or had an invalid solution tree, leaving 4,435 remaining tasks."
  ]
}